ExpressionBuilder - Class in me.zirko
ExpressionBuilder is a simple math expression API that interface with your CalculatorPanel It handles Int and Double for simple operation and scientific functions like ExpressionBuilder.sin(Double), or ExpressionBuilder.cos(Double) Here is an example of use which do "( 5 + 10 ) / 5"
